	<title>Configuring Maven project</title>


	<para>
		Here we select
		<emphasis>Create a new project</emphasis>
		which will lead us to the next screen:

		<figure>
			<title>Creating a Maven project - step 2</title>
			<mediaobject>
				<imageobject>
					<imagedata fileref="img04-create_maven_project_1.png"
						scalefit="1" width="100%" contentdepth="100%" />
				</imageobject>
			</mediaobject>
		</figure>
	</para>

	<para>
		Insert the following information in this window:

		<programlisting>
			Group Id: org.panifex
			Artifact Id: panifex-samples
			Packaging: pom
			Name: panifex-samples
		</programlisting>

		In the
		<emphasis>Parent Project</emphasis>
		section, type in:

		<programlisting>
			Group Id: org.panifex.parent.build
			Artifact Id: compiled-bundle-settings
			Version: 0.1.0-SNAPSHOT
		</programlisting>

		After clicking <emphasis>Finish</emphasis>, our project will be created.

	</para>
</section>      